Subject: [PATCH 11/11] fix: Remove redundant GPU conversion - decoder already
 outputs BGRA32Premultiplied

- Decoder outputs pixels directly in BGRA32Premultiplied format
- Previous GPU conversion was wasting cycles converting already-converted pixels
- Removed ConvertRgbaToBgraPremultipliedGpu() method from GifPlayer
- Removed unused P/Invoke binding from Interop.cs
- Both Avalonia and WPF controllers now use pixels directly from decoder
